title: Smokey Chicken & Roast Veggie Traybake with Cheddar Cheese & Smokey Aioli
description: Looks can be deceiving, this dinner may look like chicken and roast veggies but we ask you to have another glance. You may discover the gooey layer of baked Cheddar cheese over the veggies, that’s because it’s all roasted on one tray for your convenience!

